snippet.title: Chumini: Tiny Army | Reveal Trailer
snippet.description:
Here's our new game, Chumini: Tiny Army! We are currently working on it, and are planning to release it on Steam in March 2025!

This game was born as a Jam game in the Ludum Dare 56, october 2024. It's a short survivor-like in which you summon tiny creatures to battle endless waves of sylvan demons!

You can also play our other games here 👉 https://guilloteam.itch.io/

Join us!
Discord | https://discord.gg/AcQM2Awr
Bluesky | https://bsky.app/profile/guilloteam.bsky.social
TikTok | https://www.tiktok.com/@teamguillo

Original Soundtrack 🎵 | By Delphin Casado 🎹
